    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@vvo well naming it would fix my current implementation, but that would make your module less portable so says require.js documentation :) http://requirejs.org/docs/api.html#modulename generally the optomization tool should do this, but in my case it wasn't adding names for unnamed modules.\r\n\r\nWith many people moving to webpack though, in the future I'll be using that as well and this will be less of an issue. My above solution is working though going forward :)",
